id: pm-wn3r
title: Implement Ollama-aware semantic default resolution in runtime
description: "Add runtime detection/resolution so search defaults to hybrid semantic mode when local Ollama support is available, while preserving explicit configuration precedence and compatibility fallbacks."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:ollama","area:search","area:semantic",compatibility,pm-cli
