author: codex-agent
estimated_minutes: 160
acceptance_criteria: "Without explicit provider/vector config, runtime resolves Ollama-backed semantic defaults when available; search default mode becomes hybrid in that case; failures degrade safely without breaking current users."
definition_of_ready: Feature plan identifies target modules and fallback behavior expectations.
order: 1
goal: Default semantic search experience
objective: Ship safe runtime default logic
value: Out-of-box semantic behavior on compatible hosts
impact: Reduced setup friction and retained compatibility
outcome: Automatic semantic defaults with deterministic fallback
why_now: Core logic is required before tests and docs can be finalized.
