comments[2]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T13:06:35.523Z",codex-agent,Task isolates runtime behavior to keep compatibility analysis and rollback scope clear.
  "2026-04-01T13:24:18.306Z",codex-agent,"Implemented runtime Ollama semantic defaults via src/core/search/semantic-defaults.ts and wired search/reindex integration in src/cli/commands/search.ts and src/cli/commands/reindex.ts with compatibility-safe fallback in implicit default search mode. Evidence: pm test pm-wn3r --run passed both linked targeted suites; host validation in a clean PM_PATH sandbox with empty semantic settings showed pm search default mode=hybrid, pm reindex --mode semantic succeeded, and subsequent search results included matched_fields=semantic."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-01T13:06:35.523Z",codex-agent,Keep explicit settings authoritative; auto defaults must only apply when user has not configured semantic providers/stores.
